{"tid":1430293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保持獨立思考　三毛開始抹黑劉細良","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T22:43:18.000Z","uid":185990,"like":124,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d38027456bf922ab58075862494fd55be2977537","tid":1430293,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"無錯劉細良係左膠，而且有時佢講嘅嘢都會錯，但佢不嬲都戴晒頭盔話自己有可能錯，意見只供參考，亦都自認思想落後跟唔上呢次嘅運動。不過呢排好明顯有人想抹黑佢，最近嘅例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429803/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429803/page/1</a><br />\n樓主share咗呢條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/az5RaUZ7nnY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faz5RaUZ7nnY&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a4dcb375\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/az5RaUZ7nnY</a><br />\n然後藉著條片嘅標題係咁屌劉細良想做大台。然而城寨原片係呢條：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0_7MooMa8z8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0_7MooMa8z8&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=3fe25189\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0_7MooMa8z8</a><br />\n<br />\n兩條片嘅標題好明顯唔同，原片標題完全冇講大台，咁樣偷人條片再改標題到底有乜居心？我唔知樓主係咪鬼，但個youtube channel就肯定有問題。重申我唔係想吹捧劉細良，係想告誡大家，記得小心fact check。好地地有原片唔share，淨係share截圖做乜？大家記住保持獨立思考，唔好盲捧亦唔好捧撐。劉細良係過氣左膠，但佢對政府運作嘅認識應該無乜人及得上佢，雖然我都覺得佢嘅建議好多時都唔啱用，不過佢嘅資訊同分析的確參考價值。劉細良唔會係唯一一個，以後只會越嚟越多人被抹黑，我哋一定要小心分析，唔好隨便被人帶風向。"},{"pid":"d1da1c1fb61ca813c1b02a588d1841f2908bbe38","tid":1430293,"uid":185990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:58:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f11eba6171e09487afbe9d0d6cc8cb9c78f1a26f","tid":1430293,"uid":2562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L17OqaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL17OqaU.jpg&h=8e4952ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqHuCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c